{"tid":1746414,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"請教關於男女朋友相處之道","createTime":"2019-11-22T17:48:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T19:40:11.000Z","uid":60064,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8fc85514dfe5926c2b2b9543ca9dbda297ddb39d","tid":1746414,"uid":60064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T17:48:24.000Z","msg":"係咁嘅 如果巴打因為女朋友做左啲野激嬲你<br />\n你會點樣克制自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔想衰衝動講錯野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n平時我係啲好燥底嘅人 <br />\nfrd激嬲我我會直接粗口屌柒佢先<br />\n<br />\n雖然佢搞到我差啲透唔到氣聽手又震曬咁<br />\n但始終唔捨得鬧女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唯有將啲粗口收埋 語氣盡量放輕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過佢都受嘅 條氣唔多唔少都順返啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n究竟點先可以EQ高啲 冇咁易嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外想知 例如我有啲野好想佢關心多啲<br />\nor 想佢氹下我 ，但佢覺得我講笑咁<br />\n於是輕輕帶過左 應該點做<br />\n利申 已經當面講到好白 一隻字都冇少到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n心靈上好想俾你關心多啲吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好成日覺得我講笑好唔好吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申2 好珍惜佢 想行落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請巴絲指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd1a8400b227932fa7170985e47a1450175f99c9","tid":1746414,"uid":31459,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T18:01:57.000Z","msg":"你一嬲個時唔好直接屌尻佢 串佢幾句就當發洩左<br />\n利申：自己都好燥底"},{"pid":"c29960169681261c7838c7ad807482f895f519cb","tid":1746414,"uid":60064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bd1a8400b227932fa71